item_name: VICENZA VT 337 Juicer Blender Chopper Set 7 in 1 VT337
item_desc:
Blender Juicer Chopper Power Turbo 7 in 1 Vicenza VT 337

Power Blender 7in1 Vicenza VT-337
- Pemeras Jeruk
